{"tid":2308965,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"18國150議員 促林鄭確保12港人安全","createTime":"2020-12-02T08:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T08:38:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"869d9bb501a758c65292efe5497e56031489c6ae","tid":2308965,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:33:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/MQBKQB2D4JDI3IJZLWO6VWWRPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FMQBKQB2D4JDI3IJZLWO6VWWRPY%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2RA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=ed642ec3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FMQBKQB2D4JDI3IJZLWO6VWWRPY%2F&h=a22484a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/MQBKQB2D4JDI3IJZLWO6VWWRPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n18國150議員 促林鄭確保12港人安全<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1GPM_2yxJeHG8x8LundUuFVzC3A=/1536x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J6GJQFLC7FBUDJAW4LMWMEV2RE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1GPM_2yxJeHG8x8LundUuFVzC3A%3D%2F1536x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ6GJQFLC7FBUDJAW4LMWMEV2RE.jpg&h=26ada0fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■多國議員促林鄭確保12名港人得到公義；圖為日前有港人在望夫石舉「SAVE 12」燈牌。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12名港人被關押在內地逾101日，內地當局日前才宣佈移送12人到檢察院起訴。全球18個國家共150名議員聯署去信特首林鄭月娥，要求港府採取行動確保12人的安全。<br />\n<br />\n關注香港問題的人權組織「香港監察」發文指出，來自美國、英國、加拿大、澳洲、日本及歐盟等18個國家的議員，聯署去信林鄭提出四項訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提出四項訴求<br />\n<br />\n四項訴求包括要求港府採取行動、釋放12名港人，並將他們送返香港受審；允許12港人家屬委託的律師會見12人；允許12港人直接聯絡家屬；以及確保他們得到需要的藥物及醫療支援。<br />\n<br />\n多國議員聯署的公開信亦提到，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"8b3eea210cf28ac77cbb33d0c58a9bf55b6d314d","tid":2308965,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:36:30.000Z","msg":"柒婆采你有味，剩係答你干涉內政"},{"pid":"f80bc9670c5150512da455b330a1b266c546b0dc","tid":2308965,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:38:57.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接叫習近平確保?林鄭有咩權去確保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}